      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 given discretization error and code verification factors are assessed.",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error as a distinct factor (iterative convergence, round-off) is not required to be formally assessed at MRL 2 when discretization error and code verification are both assessed and met. Residuals monitored to 1e-6 for all equations; mass imbalance < 0.01%. Considered adequate for MRL 2 scope."
    },
    {
