      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; analyst qualifications and peer review process documented as sufficient control.",
      "rationale": "Use error factor formal assessment not required at MRL 2. Analyst team holds PhD-level CFD expertise with >8 years blood pump simulation experience. Simulation setup peer-reviewed by independent CFD engineer prior to production runs. Sufficient control for MRL 2 scope."
    },
    {
