      "rationale": "Test samples factor formal assessment not required at MRL 2. FDA generic pump benchmark dataset uses standardized blood analog preparation protocol (ASTM F1841). Sample preparation documentation available in FDA benchmark publication. Sufficient for MRL 2 scope."
